function AboutMe() { return (

about me

Musician + Artist + Designer + Programmer + Writer

BS, Digital Media from University of Houston
Graphic Designer, Minaret Records
DJ, KTRU 96.1
Founder, Forum Cache® + reserve® jazz publication

Art has my life and music has my heart. Exploring both through design, digital/analog technology, and language has been my focus since the mid-2010s. I'm interested in iterating/reiterating new systems for sustainable living, developing independent, self-sufficient black cultural institutions, and funding/contributing to decolonization projects. The improvisational nature of Jazz has influenced the methods in which I approach making.

Thus far, I've learned front-end web technologies (HTML + CSS + JavaScript + React), industry-standard design software (Adobe Creative Suite + Figma), and DAWs (Ableton Live + ProTools) More recently

I'm always looking for ways to expand my skillset and build my experiences. If there are any projects you'd like to share with me or collaborate on, feel free to contact me through any of the methods available in the footer.

) } export default AboutMe;
